name: Baby Saitama
description: Baby Saitama is a true community-inspired project with rewarding and deflationary tokenomics designed to provide holders with incredible value throughout the project’s continued growth and success. Baby Saitama’s three core goals are to provide holders with a valuable investment, to incorporate useful and valuable use cases for the token and the overall project ecosystem, and to use our growing success as a vehicle to give back to selected charitable organizations and causes. Please visit our website, read our whitepaper, and join our telegram groups to learn more about Baby Saitama.
